					<h1 class="text-5xl text-zinc-900 font-extrabold text-balance">
						Fluid Backgrounds
					</h1>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base text-zinc-600">
						Subtle and fluid backgrounds built with paper shaders.
					</p>
				</div>
	
				<div class="mt-12">
					<StarOnGitHub />
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>
	</main>


